{
 "name": "RPlog_SW1_Log_2000-06-10-4",
 "title": "A Word With Kartijan Lore",
 "summary": "Back in the staging area after the race, the disguised agent Bazil McKenzie (as the swooper Mege Vauki) seeks out Kartijan Lore of Team FLS, who beat his score and bumped him to third, finding her tending her own sore back near the bandaged racer Tarrin Stardiver. Bazil congratulates them both, delivers a grim rundown of the weekend's casualties -- two racers killed by the dianoga and wampa, both Pallandos hospitalized, and Altair Quila injured -- and notes that Kartijan's teammate Kestryan is up at the spaceport. Kartijan, nursing a back wrenched at the Bespin jump, invites him to continue talking in the FLS stable garage, where they chat idly about the mobility of the team's repair rigs and the strange compulsion that keeps injured racers swooping. The session winds down out of character as Kartijan disconnects for the night.",
